HI!

You can actually recompress your HDT files with these tools
--------------------------------------------------------------

1) Download any HDT file. There are plenty of them right here:  http://www.rdfhdt.org/datasets/

2) To convert the RDF/HDT file to RDF/HDT++:
	> [HDT++ Path]/tools/hdt2hdtpp yourfile.hdt yourfile.hdtpp
